OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy throughout the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with frequent showers, some
OL,8,Fof these heavy at times and
OL,9,Foccasionally forming longer spells of
OL,10,Frain. Windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy and breezy with
OL,13,Fshowers, heavy and forming longer
OL,14,Fspells of rain at times. Rain and
OL,15,Fstrong winds gradually easing later in
OL,16,Fthe day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
