OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry on Sunday and Monday with some
OL,7,Flong spells of sunshine. Some rain
OL,8,Fspreading northeast later Monday.
OL,9,FCloudy on Tuesday with rain or
OL,10,Fshowers. Becoming warmer.
